### IA Integration API Tests
### Usage: Copy these requests into VS Code REST Client or Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@workspaceId = your-workspace-id

### Get IA Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ia/status

### Chat - Single Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ia/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Combien de dossiers ai-je actuellement?"
    }
  ]
}

### Chat - Multi-turn Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ia/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Bonjour! Peux-tu me donner un résumé?"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Bonjour! Je surveille vos dossiers actifs. Vous en avez actuellement 12."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Combien sont urgents?"
    }
  ]
}

### Chat - With Context
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ia/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Quelles sont les alertes importantes?"
    }
  ]
}

### Analyze Dossier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ia/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dossierId": "clsk123abc456"
}

### Suggest Alerts
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ia/suggest-alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Generate Realistic Render
